body:
So I bought the new skin for Gnar a few days back (as I always do) and I noticed something. I really love the skin itself but there's a problem with the sound when mini Gnar is about to tranform into MEGA Gnar. There is almost no sound compared to his other skins. The sound is a great way for the player to tell when exactly Gnar is gonna transform, since the sound is timed with his passive. But with this skin you don't have that.

Thank you for your time. 
Gaffz {{champion:150}}
